Stanford Investment Group, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:19 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Stanford Investment Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Stanford Investment Group, Inc. is a private equity firm specializing in management buyouts, corporate divestitures, recapitalizations, turnarounds, PIPES, and co-investments in middle market companies. The firm seeks to invest in business services, healthcare products and services, consumable products, niche manufacturing, logistics, industrial outsourcing, and disruptive technologies and processes. It primarily invests in the Eastern United States for smaller companies and throughout the United States, Canada, and Mexico for larger companies. The firm typically invests in companies with revenues between $5 million and $250 million and EBITDA between $1 million and $20 million. It will cons...
Stanford Investment Group, Inc. is a private equity firm specializing in management buyouts, corporate divestitures, recapitalizations, turnarounds, PIPES, and co-investments in middle market companies. The firm seeks to invest in business services, healthcare products and services, consumable products, niche manufacturing, logistics, industrial outsourcing, and disruptive technologies and processes. It primarily invests in the Eastern United States for smaller companies and throughout the United States, Canada, and Mexico for larger companies. The firm typically invests in companies with revenues between $5 million and $250 million and EBITDA between $1 million and $20 million. It will consider distressed and underperforming companies requiring strategic and operational changes in addition to capital. Stanford Investment Group, Inc. was founded in 1990 and is based in New York, New York with an additional office in Ridgewood, New Jersey.
Detailed Description


1285 Avenue of AmericasSuite 3500New York, NY 10019United StatesFounded in 1990



www.stanfordinvgroup.com







